Hellplague/ Malice:
 
Hellplague had enjoyed the action to this point.  But when Malice started his little mind game, she lost her interest and began to get a little jealous of her sister.  She walked up to the two and tried to shake Malice out of it.
 
Malice relished the moment, until Hellplague interrupted.  He reluctantly broke the kiss, but did not look to Hellplague.
"Hello?  Is Malice even home today?" Hellplague said, trying to get the male's attention.
